- The boss wants us to do the launch.

04:14.254 --> 04:16.837
Families? Not my strong point.

04:17.048 --> 04:19.709
- Why are you dressed like that?
- Company match.

04:19.843 --> 04:22.301
I'm second,
if I score today, I'll be first.

