I'm no longer sure.

34:19.975 --> 34:22.467
<i>- Luca?
- I think I found what we're after.</i>

34:23.853 --> 34:26.641
<i>- Luca Pastore?
- Bibi?</i>

34:26.856 --> 34:28.722
Hold on, I'll call you back.

34:32.027 --> 34:33.985
How did you know?

34:34.947 --> 34:37.440
