that I frankly don't approve of.

36:01.451 --> 36:03.613
Did you order meat?

36:04.621 --> 36:06.658
- Carpaccio.
- Good.

36:18.802 --> 36:21.419
Who the hell is Luigi Brancato?

36:22.180 --> 36:26.265
