Your mother, your brother...

37:03.430 --> 37:07.094
- Are you threatening me?
- Are you stupid?

37:07.475 --> 37:09.307
I'm not the one threatening you.

37:09.561 --> 37:13.145
Do you realize who the hell
we're dealing with?

37:13.231 --> 37:16.394
I don't give a shit, I'll talk!

37:16.693 --> 37:18.650
I'm not scared.

37:40.258 --> 37:41.748
Leo!

37:41.968 --> 37:43.629
- My friend, welcome.
- Thanks.

37:44.429 --> 37:46.386
This is Assia...

37:46.681 --> 37:49.048
- And Teresa.
- Hi, I'm Leonardo.

37:49.434 --> 37:50.890
Leo.

37:51.227 --> 37:55.061
Keep Leo company,
you come with me. Have fun!

37:55.273 --> 37:58.015
- Isn't your neighbor coming?
- Berlusconi?

37:58.234 --> 38:00.225
Who knows!

38:03.823 --> 38:07.657
- Shall we have a drink?
- Yes, I'd like that.

38:11.414 --> 38:13.121
Excuse me.

38:15.210 --> 38:16.917
Angelica?

38:17.712 --> 38:19.077
