45:45.117 --> 45:48.235
<i>this terrible, difficult,
anguished atmosphere</i>

45:48.454 --> 45:51.822
<i>which began when
the first reports arrived</i>

45:52.041 --> 45:55.204
<i>regarding the news of the attack
