47:15.624 --> 47:17.615
Well...

47:18.461 --> 47:21.624
I'll go back to my girl,
look how hot she is!

47:23.841 --> 47:26.629
I bring her here,
so no one will bother her.

47:26.844 --> 47:28.255
They're all queers.

47:29.055 --> 47:30.341
Here?

47:31.891 --> 47:33.677
See you in Parliament.

47:33.893 --> 47:36.385
Shit. I got you!

47:36.604 --> 47:38.436
- Bye.
- Bye, Bortolotti!

47:38.856 --> 47:40.597
Bye. bye.

47:44.153 --> 47:47.111
Well, shall we go for a dip?

47:53.371 --> 47:55.578
