- Which "politicized judges"?

50:54.218 --> 50:55.708
Thank you.

50:57.054 --> 51:00.137
Please. Please!

51:22.413 --> 51:24.450
- Did you sleep with her?
- What?

51:25.249 --> 51:27.707
Did you sleep with Amanda?

51:28.460 --> 51:30.622
