don't have a goddamn clue.

52:02.620 --> 52:05.783
Here, a present for Barbara.

52:07.625 --> 52:09.457
Have fun.

52:09.627 --> 52:12.244
Right, it'll be a ball.

52:17.092 --> 52:18.503
Viola!

53:30.999 --> 53:32.865
Come to daddy.

53:33.210 --> 53:35.793
So, I have a joke to tell you.

53:36.839 --> 53:38.250
Sit down.

53:38.424 --> 53:42.509
Berlusconi suddenly walks into a room,
his wife jumps up and shouts:

53:42.720 --> 53:46.839
"Oh God!", and he says:
"Relax, just call me Silvio".

53:50.853 --> 53:53.220
Was I good?

53:54.940 --> 53:57.102
Shall I tell you another one?

53:58.652 --> 54:00.643
Good evening, sir.

54:01.155 --> 54:03.943
- I'm Viola's father.
